@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000

### Health check via list events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events

### Create event
# @name createEvent
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Teatro da Primavera",
  "type": "TEATRO",
  "dateTime": "2026-05-20T20:00:00",
  "startingSales": "2026-05-01T08:00:00",
  "endingSales": "2026-05-19T23:00:00",
  "price": 85.5
}

### Captura o ID criado
@eventId = {{createEvent.response.body.id}}

### Get event by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}

### Update event
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Teste de venda de curso de programação",
