}

### List sales
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales

### Create sale
# @name createSale
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "92ff4138-3ae5-4282-a918-46a663c17629",
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "status": "EM_ABERTO"
}

### Captura o ID da venda criada
@saleId = {{createSale.response.body.id}}

### Get sale by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales/{{saleId}}

### Update sale
PUT {{baseUrl}}/sales/{{saleId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "92ff4138-3ae5-4282-a918-46a663c17629",
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "status": "PAGO"
}

### Delete sale
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/sales/{{saleId}}

### Delete event (deixe por último pode causar erros se rodar antes)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}
